nitiativen von Provinzial-Ständen, Städten und Gemeinden, die Tätigkeit der Behörden, die öffentliche Meinung und die Bedeutung der Medien. Sie bestätigen die in der neueren Forschung unstrittige Ansicht, dass die Geschichte der preußischen Monarchie im 19. Jahrhundert keine Geschichte des kontinuierlichen Niedergangs war.  aRoyal voyages were an effective means of representing monarchic rule. This volume presents for the first time an edition of archival sources on the domestic and foreign travels by Prussian monarchs between 1797 and 1871. The sources illustrate the political, economic, and cultural impact of these trips in the Prussian provinces along with their perception by the inhabitants of cities and small towns.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aPolitics and culturezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy19th centuryvSources. 0aPolitics and culturezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy19th century. 0aPolitics and culturezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy20th centuryvSources. 0aPolitics and culturezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy20th century. 4a19. Jahrhundert. 4a19th century. 4aMonarchie. 4aPreußen. 4aPrussia. 4aReisen. 4aRepresentation. 4aRepräsentation. 4amonarchy. 4atravels. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Germany.2bisacsh1 aBBAW, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHuch, Gaby, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aNeugebauer, Wolfgang, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2016z9783110485189oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831104093380 cprintz978311040915440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/97